{"TopicId":178978,"ForumId":46,"TopicTitle":"Forum editor tables","CreatedByName":"vitekc45c","CreatedById":98257,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-10-15T14:08:57Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"vitekc45c","CreatedById":98257,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-10-15T14:08:58Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHow. Do. They. Work.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Geonovast","CreatedById":179753,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-10-15T14:38:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027ve found them pretty straightforward.\u00A0 Is there something specific you\u0027re having issues with?\u00A0 You should be able to just click the table button in the editor, tell it how big you want the table, then enter the info into each box.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ctable border=\u00221\u0022 cellpadding=\u00221\u0022 cellspacing=\u00221\u0022 style=\u0022width:500px;\u0022\u003E\u003Ccaption\u003E\nTable!\n\u003C/caption\u003E\n\u003Ctbody\u003E\u003Ctr\u003E\u003Ctd\u003E\nColors\n\u003C/td\u003E\n\u003Ctd\u003E\nShapes\n\u003C/td\u003E\n\u003C/tr\u003E\u003Ctr\u003E\u003Ctd\u003E\nRed\n\u003C/td\u003E\n\u003Ctd\u003E\nSquare\n\u003C/td\u003E\n\u003C/tr\u003E\u003Ctr\u003E\u003Ctd\u003E\nBlue\n\u003C/td\u003E\n\u003Ctd\u003E\nCircle\n\u003C/td\u003E\n\u003C/tr\u003E\u003C/tbody\u003E\u003C/table\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"bewing","CreatedById":154251,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-10-15T14:38:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n(ninja\u0027d by Geonovast)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222018-10-15T14:40:02Z\u0022 title=\u002210/15/2018 02:40  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00225 yr\u0022\u003EOctober 15, 2018\u003C/time\u003E by bewing\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"vitekc45c","CreatedById":98257,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-10-15T14:42:46Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks, figured it out: you cant change number of rows and colum after you create the table, and you neet to ctrl-right clict to open a menu to delete the table AND you cant create new lines after the table...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOh, how I miss the days of code based forum editors. None of this un-intuitive interactive-graphical nonsence........\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Geonovast","CreatedById":179753,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-10-15T14:43:40Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223468116\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022178978\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221539614566\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002298257\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022vitekc45c\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, vitekc45c said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nyou cant change number of rows and colum after you create the table\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYeah that\u0027s always bothered me.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"sumghai","CreatedById":66272,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-10-15T20:48:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#27ae60;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003E[MOD - Moved to Kerbal Network subforum, as this is a question about posting on the forums rather than the game itself]\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}